fields.challenge_text: Connect to the Wifi (WLAN) or Hotspot of something. Be sure that you can connect to the internet! (Your team is not allowed to give a Hotspot for each other)

fields.challenge_text: Close your eyes, spin in a circle at least 7 times and come to a stop. Walk into that direction for 100 normal steps. If you are not able to, discard this challenge.
